high_descs: turn around and walk over to the sink at the end of the kitchen counter space on the right
grab an egg out of the right side of the sink there
turn right and walk over to the fridge on the left just up ahead
place the egg inside the fridge to cool, then take it back out
turn left and walk over to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter to the left of the fridge, turn to face the coffee maker
place the egg down on the kitchen counter there in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a cooled egg on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn around and walk ahead, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the egg in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the egg on the left side of the fridge, to the right of the potato. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the egg out again.
Place the egg on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the counter, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Take the egg out of the sink basin.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the egg inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled egg then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave, then turn right to face the coffee machine on the counter.
Put the chilled egg on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg on the counter.
